Kafka Commands Used (Recent Session)

---

**1️⃣ Kafka Broker / Server**

```
bin\windows\kafka-server-start.bat config\server.properties
```

---

**2️⃣ Topic Commands**

* Create topic:

```
bin\windows\kafka-topics.bat --create --topic user-topic --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
bin\windows\kafka-topics.bat --create --topic quickstart-events --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
```

* List topics (optional):

```
bin\windows\kafka-topics.bat --list --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
```

---

**3️⃣ Producer Commands**

```
bin\windows\kafka-console-producer.bat --topic quickstart-events --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
```

* Example messages sent:

```
hello bro
Hi
How Are you
Hello bhai
kaise ho
```

---

**4️⃣ Consumer Commands**

```
bin\windows\kafka-console-consumer.bat --topic user-topic --from-beginning --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
bin\windows\kafka-console-consumer.bat --topic quickstart-events --from-beginning --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
```

* Example messages received:

```
hello bro
Hi
How Are you
Hellow
Hello bhai
kaise ho
good morning
...
```
